high_descs: walk over to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter
grab the cup from underneath the coffee maker
walk on over to the fridge
put the cup inside the fridge to cool, then take it back out again
walk back over to the coffee maker
put the coffee cup under the spout of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: cool the coffee cup underneath the coffee maker

high_descs: Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the coffee pot.
Pick up the cup on the coffee maker.
Turn right and then turn left.  Go to the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Put the coffee cup on the top shelf to the right of the pan.  Close the fridge. Open the fridge and grab the coffee cup. Close the fridge.
Turn around and go towards the sink.  turn left at the coffee maker.
Place the coffee cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Get coffee cup to put in fridge to put on the coffee maker.
